    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle x}</annotatio=
n>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/87f9e315fd7e2ba406057a97300593c4802b53e4" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.33ex; height:1.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle x}">=
