<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Functions">Functions</h2><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DSet_(mathematics)&=
amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D12" title=3D"Edit section: Functions"><span=
>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div=
>
<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
Main article: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Function_(mathematic=
s)" title=3D"Function (mathematics)">Function (mathematics)</a></div>
<p>A <i>function</i>  from a set <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font=
-style:italic;">A</span>=E2=80=94the <i>domain</i>=E2=80=94to a set <span c=
lass=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">B</span>=E2=80=94the <i>=
codomain</i>=E2=80=94is a rule that assigns to each element of <span class=
=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">A</span> a unique element of=
 <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">B</span>. For ex=
ample, the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Square_function" class=
=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Square function">square function</a> maps every r=
eal number <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</spa=
n> to <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>x</i><sup>2</sup></span>. Functions can be=
 formally defined in terms of sets by means of their <a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Graph_of_a_function" title=3D"Graph of a function">graph=
</a>, which are subsets of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Car=
tesian_product" title=3D"Cartesian product">Cartesian product</a> (see belo=
w) of the domain and the codomain.=20
</p><p>Functions are fundamental for set theory, and examples are given in =
following sections.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Indexed_families">Indexed f=
amilies</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-br=
